    {
      "content": "The system can continue its normal operation if there is power loss to one of its power supplies.",
      "pos": [
        7607,
        7704
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "However, to ensure high availability of the device, restore power to the power supply as soon as possible.",
      "pos": [
