        7811
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If there is a power outage or power interruption on both power supplies, the system will shut down in an orderly and controlled manner.",
      "pos": [
        7813,
        7948
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "When the power is restored, the system will automatically turn on.",
